						<a href="/portale/it.html" title="torna alla homepage INAIL"><img class="logo-menu" alt="Logo Inail" src="/etc.clientlibs/alma-inail-hub-foundation/clientlibs/clientlib-base/resources/img/logo-inail.svg"/>
						</a>
